{"tid":413025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【小一報名】雙非家長特意遲一年報讀：操佢變大B 細B冇優勢","createTime":"2017-09-25T07:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T08:36:05.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f397afdda22288d4413a896e6a2c8f4900082f34","tid":413025,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:27:13.000Z","msg":"2018／19學年的小一「自行分配學位」收生程序今日展開，此學年是最後一批「雙非」學童入學期。有「雙非」家長一早已安排子女入讀上水的幼稚園，亦打算在港報讀小一，今早前往上水惠州公立學校交表。早上9時已有近20名家長前來報名，「雙非」家長羅太指，家住深圳福田區，兒子現在每日花近一小時，到上水入讀幼稚園，，「佢都習慣咗跨境返學，亦都完全無考慮（回深圳讀書），本來喺香港生，就係覺得呢邊教育制度好，為咗香港教育、文化、各方面都好啲，比較國際化啲，比起大陸亦比較接軌得多啲」。<br />\n<br />\n羅太趕上「雙非尾班車」，惟她笑指兒子2011年尾出生，上年亦可入學，惟決定今年才為他報小一，「因為太細個，男仔都係後期發育，咁變咗細B就乜嘢優勢都無喇，所以就操佢變成大B先」，對兒子的能力有信心，不擔心競爭。<br />\n<br />\n尹小姐亦為「雙非」家長，今早花個半小時、8時已來到香港排隊交表，她指不擔心小孩跨境讀書，「快的花一小時就可以，（不怕辛苦嗎？）不怕，因為有校車吧」，惟她指如小孩入學，亦會考慮租上水單位居住；她又指欣賞香港的教育制度，亦為小孩報讀英文、畫畫等興趣班，預備入學。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170925/large/1506308151_1a2b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170925%2Flarge%2F1506308151_1a2b.jpg&h=dc659e5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">羅太(左)指兒子上年亦可入學，惟決定今年才為他報小一。尹小姐(右)不擔心小孩跨境讀書。 (王心義攝)</span><br />\n<br />\n大陸閪有樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170925/57252290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170925%2F57252290&d=yT8x7Aq%2F5ss%2Bamssk%2Fwf8TANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=fc527ebd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170925%2F57252290&h=5ea994f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170925/57252290</a>"},{"pid":"a1f4d76b2f04b75de55955ecb489c368bd07cd9c","tid":413025,"uid":135313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:29:26.000Z","msg":"蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f97414a60918cbb75ece545510e55b5a15d688","tid":413025,"uid":36178,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:29:30.000Z","msg":"dna嘅嘢, 支那蝗識條春<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ee6679c00876e107b11a0a2df76bd5d464152a","tid":413025,"uid":522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:33:27.000Z","msg":"大陸人真係有樣睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  d輪廓"},{"pid":"d6f5e3ed049b3008243098453d18c13dba08194d","tid":413025,"uid":58551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:35:52.000Z","msg":"點解佢哋d樣寧舍老同怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f901a904530e6f28c97f2083ccafb7626f8ce199","tid":413025,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T07:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解佢哋d樣寧舍老同怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n元素周期表<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fea9616055e1a5a04b66f12b9f329929bf62ef","tid":413025,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:10:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc5d991d436a8628d4144a1980b4ad189396685c","tid":413025,"uid":2521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"真係明符其實，操佢媽B"},{"pid":"9e1beeca47f7ac94339a7963902348600062621c","tid":413025,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T08:36:05.000Z","msg":"到底炎黃賤種有幾自私先可以破壞人地公平制度"}]}